  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK711">
<l>avaiyaṟin tārāyntu colluka colliṉ</l>
<l>ṟokaiyaṟinta tūymai yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let the pure who know the arrangement of words speak with deliberation after ascertaining (the nature of) the court (then assembled).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
